text:
I got your card!
I was surprised
you attached a present!
I can't believe it fit
through the mail!

I had fun reading your card!
It was full of words. And a present!
I'm gonna send you a present too!
It's part of this message,
in case you were wondering.

Thanks for the card!
And your present!
Sorry I'm writing slow right now.
I am eating snacks. I hope it
reads faster than I wrote it.
Oh! Here's a present for you too!

I loved the card
you sent me! I've been
reading it every day!
I'm going to keep reading
it until I can recite it
from memory!

Thanks for the card!
I read it all the
way to the end!
I would love it
if you sent another!
I'll be waiting!

I was so surprised by your card!
I loved it! I read it while
eating some snacks.
Send another if ya wanna!
